AUDIO: 'just click on this download icon. This will download the model into your normal downloads folder, which means the file stays saved on your phone forever unless you delete it manually. Once the model is downloaded, just click on this import'

[02:05] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'icon, select the model file you downloaded, and the app will automatically import it for you. And yep, the model is now imported successfully. All of your downloaded models will appear right here in the'

